a:5:{s:5:"title";s:54:"Attio ships a bundle of platform and design updates";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:829:"<p>Attio’s update includes multiple small-to-mid changes across workspace settings, billing, referrals, and file handling.</p>
<h3>What changed</h3>
<p>Attio now allows slug reuse for deleted workspaces, adds a configurable workspace accent color, and streamlines billing flows for plan selection, extra invites, automation credits, and checkout. Referral tooling was updated with a new CTA, revamped Refer and earn page, quick-share links with preset copy, and an anonymized referral list with status indicators.</p>
<h3>Files and attachments</h3>
<p>Attio also redesigned file storage: refreshed Files tab UI, migration to an S3-style backend, attachment support across all record types (including Deals), and improved image rendering. A small site UI tweak allows copying the logo as an SVG via hover.</p>
";s:9:"text-flow";a:5:{i:0;s:121:"Attio’s update includes multiple small-to-mid changes across workspace settings, billing, referrals, and file handling.";i:1;a:2:{i:0;s:2:"h2";i:1;s:12:"What changed";}i:2;s:361:"Attio now allows slug reuse for deleted workspaces, adds a configurable workspace accent color, and streamlines billing flows for plan selection, extra invites, automation credits, and checkout. Referral tooling was updated with a new CTA, revamped Refer and earn page, quick-share links with preset copy, and an anonymized referral list with status indicators.";i:3;a:2:{i:0;s:2:"h2";i:1;s:21:"Files and attachments";}i:4;s:252:"Attio also redesigned file storage: refreshed Files tab UI, migration to an S3-style backend, attachment support across all record types (including Deals), and improved image rendering. A small site UI tweak allows copying the logo as an SVG via hover.";}s:4:"meta";a:2:{s:14:"links-required";a:0:{}s:18:"resources-detected";a:0:{}}}s:7:"summary";s:87:"Attio ships a bundle of platform and design updates | Read fresh CRM news on WeekCRM";s:14:"comments-count";i:0;s:9:"tags-data";a:2:{s:5:"ctree";a:3:{i:0;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:5:"attio";s:4:"href";s:35:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/attio/";}i:1;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:3:"CRM";s:4:"href";s:33:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/crm/";}i:2;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:15:"product updates";s:4:"href";s:45:"http://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/product-updates/";}}s:20:"all-resnames-uploads";a:0:{}}}